# Security Policy

## Supported Versions

| Version | Supported |
| ------- | --------- |
| v1.x    | ✅         |
| Older   | ❌         |

## Reporting a Vulnerability

If you discover a security vulnerability, please report it through **GitHub**'s private vulnerability [reporting system](https://gitlab.com/kilianpaquier/gitlab-storage-cleaner/security/advisories/new).
